OL,3,CFour mayoral elections could be
OL,4,Cpostponed for another 2 years
OL,6,FElections in nine council areas,
OL,7,Fincluding six in the Meridian region:
OL,8,FEast Sussex, West Sussex, Essex,
OL,9,FHampshire, the Isle of Wight and
OL,10,FSurrey, were postponed to 2026 amid
OL,11,Fthe reorganisation of local government
OL,12,Fin England.
OL,14,FReform UK enjoyed success in the local
OL,15,Felections in May, winning a majority
OL,16,Fin Kent and seats in Oxfordshire and
OL,17,FWiltshire.
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,20,Fand Local Government has declined to
OL,21,Fcomment.
